                "invention-title": [
                    "Ammonia-hydrogen fusion zero-carbon burner",
                    "一种氨氢融合零碳燃烧器"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an ammonia-hydrogen fusion zero-carbon combustor which comprises a combustion chamber, a flue gas circulating pipeline, a graded preheating device, a heat pipe heat exchange device and a combustion-supporting gas rotational flow device. Through a strong rotational flow proportioning method, a combustion-supporting gas rotational flow device is arranged, and air distribution is improved in an arrangement mode of high and low rotational flow numbers and axial and longitudinal rotational flow numbers, so that mixing is enhanced; the heat of high-temperature flue gas is fully and efficiently utilized, the loss of high-quality heat energy is avoided to a certain extent, the effects of energy conservation and emission reduction are achieved, and the requirements of a user for energy conservation, cleanness, safety and stability in combustion of ammonia gas can be met; hydrogen-rich gas is adopted as fuel, H2 diffusion on-duty flames are arranged in the center of the combustion chamber, and the flame stabilizing effect can be achieved. The heat pipe heat exchanger, the combustion-supporting gas rotational flow device and other devices are matched for use, so that the problems that the ignition temperature of ammonia gas is high, the ignition time is long, ignition is not easy, and ammonia combustion is unstable are solved; the method is high in economical efficiency and high in adjustability, and meets the goals of carbon reduction and zero-carbon production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氨氢融合零碳燃烧器，包括燃烧室、烟气循环管道、分级预热装置、热管换热装置和助燃气体旋流装置。通过强旋流配比的方法，设置助燃气体旋流装置，使用高低旋流数和轴向纵向旋流数布置方式来提高配风，从而加强混合；充分、高效地利用了高温烟气的热量，一定程度上避免了高品质热能的损失，起到了节能、减排的作用，可满足用户节能、清洁、安全稳定燃烧氨气的需求；采用富氢气体作为燃料，在燃烧室中心设置H2扩散值班火焰，可以达到稳焰的效果；通过热管换热器、助燃气体旋流装置等装置的配合使用，解决了氨气着火温度高，着火时间长，不易点燃和氨燃烧不稳定的问题；发明经济性高，可调节性高，符合减碳、零碳生产的目标。"
                }
